About the job
We are seeking a detail-oriented and proactive Entry-Level Quality Assurance Engineer to join our team and help ensure the delivery of high-quality software solutions. The ideal candidate will have a strong understanding of software development lifecycles, testing methodologies, and quality standards. This role involves designing, executing, and maintaining test plans, test cases, and automated test scripts to identify defects and ensure functionality meets specifications.
The QA Engineer will collaborate closely with developers, product managers, and other stakeholders to validate software performance, usability, and reliability. Proficiency in testing tools, bug tracking systems, and basic scripting is essential. Analytical thinking, problem-solving abilities, and meticulous attention to detail are key to identifying potential issues and ensuring software meets quality expectations.
Effective communication and teamwork are crucial, as the candidate will contribute to cross-functional discussions, provide feedback, and assist in documenting test results and improvement recommendations. Intellectual curiosity, adaptability, and a commitment to continuous learning are highly valued, with a focus on understanding emerging technologies, best practices, and industry standards.
This role offers the opportunity to gain hands-on experience with software testing, contribute directly to product quality, and grow within a collaborative environment dedicated to innovation, reliability, and delivering exceptional user experiences.

